 <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/ukaldravox.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kaldravox</A> at: 6/4/02 5:16:56 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/binfinitusvindicat.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=arciteizuber>Arcite iz uber</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(6/4/02 6:20:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19.topic&index=31>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Legalization of Marijuana: Good or Bad?</span><hr size=1> It's not addicting, and there is a good reason people use it every day.<br>
They're weak minded.<br>
<br>
Want to know the last time I smoked pot?<br>
At least a month ago.<br>
<br>
That may not *seem* like a long time, but it's sure not every day.  I don't wake up and say &quot;oh god, i need a hit.  where is my bong?!&quot;  And believe me, I know people who are like that.  They start the day with a bong hit -- bad idea.<br>
<br>
And yeah, those activities are more fun while high.  Doesn't mean I don't do them sober.  I went swimming today.  I go snowboarding three times a week (when it's the season).  I love riding my bike up in the mountains.  I've done all those things while I was high -- but I've done them much much more sober.<br>
<br>
From what I understand (speaking to Mork now), while comparing a joint to a cigarette, the joint is actually worse for you (in regards to lung cancer).  <br>
<br>
But here's the catch --<br>
How many cigarettes do you have to smoke to GET lung cancer?  500,000? A million?  Am I exaggerating?  I dunno, I might be, I have no idea how many it takes.  My point is though, you don't chain smoke joints.  You smoke one, and that's usually it for the night.  You don't smoke 10 joints in 20 minutes, like you do with cigarettes.<br>
<br>
I'm not sure if this is actually true (whether or not a joint is worse than a cigarette), but even if it is, like I say, you don't smoke 2 packs of joints  day.<br>
<br>
As to Marijuana leading to &quot;harder&quot; drugs.  That's a load of bull.  Again, it's weak minded people who gotta &quot;get a better high&quot; or whatever.  Personally?  I've tried (not abuse, but yes tried once) pretty much every drug under the sun.  Most I didn't care for, and the one time was all I did.  I'm a big believer in trying everything once though, because life is short, you know the spiel.  I did the &quot;harder&quot; stuff before I ever even touched weed.  So maybe you could say the harder stuff leads to Marijuana. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm9.showNextMessage?topicID=19.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.infinitusvindicat.com/images/f_addreply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm9.emailToFriend?topicID=19.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm9.threadControl?topicID=19.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm9.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=19.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm9.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=19.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub79.ezboard.com/BBSF